{"tid":2045481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"由職工盟獲美工會頒人權獎看香港人於國際戰線上的幼稚","createTime":"2020-06-01T00:09:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T02:06:15.000Z","uid":26770,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9cb5d53fc13059cf00b7388158182be19df88bf9","tid":2045481,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T00:09:26.000Z","msg":"1該組織(AFL-CIO)實際係美國民主黨地盤<br />\n香港人成日當自己係共和黨護法攻擊民主黨係好幼稚<br />\n美國民主黨都有份幫香港人, 香港人需要的係<ins>美國國家勢力</ins>的支持,而唔係介入別人的政治玩黨爭<br />\n<br />\n2 講攪活動支援明尼蘇達州示威者更加白痴<br />\n<ins>67暴動市民支持鎮壓係因為左仔殘害人民</ins><br />\n<br />\n而香港示威者一直係國際上係受害人光環, 遭香港警魔強刑,私刑, 用車撞<br />\n<ins>而美國人就算反對警暴, 對明尼蘇達州示威者都未必支持</ins><br />\n<br />\n<ins>有好多人就話講清楚支持咩位就ok<br />\n係討論區比機會你慢慢整理依然1999<br />\n你覺得自己有料係外國記者前表達清楚而唔奶野?</ins>"},{"pid":"dd2173452e8ae5cbaddc91d5d1d5155cbfa88e6c","tid":2045481,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T00:13:53.000Z","msg":"仲有班人平時連咩叫Antifa都唔知<br />\n格硬套香港黃絲藍絲果套野落去<br />\n<br />\n<ins>分析政治你首先唔該學下美國史</ins><br />\n而唔係隨便代入黃絲藍絲, 格硬套用香港政治,咩正義對邪惡落去"},{"pid":"e6741c0851ac3a4e402ec418bb82bdb976ba0e0b","tid":2045481,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T00:32:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s3reRMt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs3reRMt.png&h=574aa3e7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n狂出假acc呃香港示威者介入<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2045468/page/3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2045468/page/3</a>"},{"pid":"6cdc47fc9c4684cefadbb6eb44f796d93a1983ca","tid":2045481,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T02:06:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />兩黨都喺香港議題上支持香港人<br />\n唔係兩黨合作香港人權與民主法案邊有咁快過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌民主黨又有咩用"}]}